PrecisAmendments to the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS (Schedule No. 897) which update the compositional requirements for foods for use in weight reduction diets to reflect Health Canada's current nutritional recommendations and broaden the range of products allowed to be represented or sold for weight reduction diets to include foods sold at weight loss clinics.
